# Instructions for Running Tests

## Running Tests

### General
- `pytest -xsv tests/` for running all unit and integration tests.
- `pytest -xsv tests/ --cov=ipybox --cov-report=term` for running all unit and integration tests and generating a coverage report.

### Unit Tests
- `pytest -xsv tests/unit` for running unit tests.
- `pytest -xsv tests/unit --cov=ipybox --cov-report=term` for running unit tests and generating a coverage report.

### Integration Tests
- `pytest -xsv tests/integration` for running all integration tests.
- `pytest -xsv tests/integration --cov=ipybox --cov-report=term` for running all integration tests and generating a coverage report.
- `pytest -xsv tests/integration/test_[name].py` for running a single integration test file.
- `pytest -xsv tests/integration/test_[name].py::[test-name]` for running a single integration test.
